## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of resource allocation practices across different industries. The information is also limited to the data available up to October 2023, and newer practices or insights may not be included. Additionally, the perspectives provided are primarily from Western project management frameworks and may not fully represent global practices.